'''第79届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2006年电影|2006年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2007年2月25日下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上20点30分）在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发了24座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过{{lang|en|[[美国广播公司|ABC]]}}在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由劳拉·泽斯金担任制片人，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨导演，女演员[[艾伦·德杰尼勒斯|艾伦·德杰尼勒斯]]首次担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2008-09-07 | title = Ellen, meet Oscar | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2006-09-07-degeneres-host_x.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221065805/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2006-09-07-degeneres-host_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | archivedate = 2014-02-21}}</ref>。两个星期前的2月10日，另一位女演员[[玛吉·吉伦哈尔|玛吉·吉伦哈尔]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利山威尔希尔酒店|比佛利山威尔希尔酒店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Rich | first = Joshua | title = Maggie G. Hosts Sci/Tech Oscars | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/07/maggie_g_hosts_/ | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = TimeWarner |date = 2007-02-07 | archivedate = 2013-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131202225234/http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/07/maggie_g_hosts_/}}</ref>。

《[[无间道风云|无间道风云]]》赢得了包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]在内的四项大奖，是这个夜晚的最大赢家<ref>{{cite news | last = Halbfinger | first = David M. | last2 = Waxman | first2 = Sharon | title = 'The Departed' Wins Best Picture, Scorsese Best Director | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2007-02-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140310234020/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/02/26/movies/awardsseason/26osca.html?pagewanted=all&_r=1& | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/02/26/movies/awardsseason/26osca.html?pagewanted=all&_r=1& | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = The New York Times | archivedate = 2014-03-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = At Long Last, Scorsese Wins Oscar | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/at-long-last-scorsese-wins-oscar/ | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = CBS News | publisher = CBS Corporation | date = 2009-02-11 | archivedate = 2014-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140515151121/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/at-long-last-scorsese-wins-oscar/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括胜出三项的《[[潘神的迷宫|潘神的迷宫]]》，获奖两项的《[[难以忽视的真相|难以忽视的真相]]》、《[[梦女孩|梦女孩]]》和《[[阳光小美女|阳光小美女]]》，以及胜出一项的《[[通天塔_(电影)|通天塔]]》、《[[颍州的孩子|颍州的孩子]]》、《[[丹麦诗人|丹麦诗人]]》（{{lang|en|''The Danish Poet''}}）、《[[快乐的大脚|快乐的大脚]]》、《[[末代独裁|末代独裁]]》、《[[硫磺岛的来信|硫磺岛的来信]]》、《[[窃听风暴|窃听风暴]]》、《[[绝代艳后|绝代艳后]]》、《[[加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺|加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺]]》、《[[女王_(电影)|女王]]》和《[[西岸故事|西岸故事]]》（{{lang|en|''West Bank Story''}}）。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了近四千万美国观众收看。

== 获奖和提名 ==
第79届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单于2007年1月23日由学院主席希德·甘尼斯（{{lang|en|Sid Ganis}}）和女演员[[萨尔玛·海耶克|萨尔玛·海耶克]]一起在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布<ref>{{cite news | last = Stein | first = Ruthe | title = Sure, the film business is cutthroat, but it also has heart, says industry leader Sid Ganis, who seems to have a lot of heart himself | work = The San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Hearst Corporation | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202225255/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Sure-the-film-business-is-cutthroat-but-it-also-2655088.php | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | date = 2007-01-22 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Sure-the-film-business-is-cutthroat-but-it-also-2655088.php}}</ref>。《梦女孩》以8项提名领跑，《通天塔》以7项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news | last = Kaufman | first = Gil | title = 'Dreamgirls' Leads Oscar Noms — Without Best Picture Or Beyonce | work = MTV | publisher = Viacom Media Networks | date = 2007-01-23 | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/1550536/dreamgirls-leads-oscar-noms-without-best-picture-or-beyonce/ | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | archivedate = 2014-05-15  | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140515154227/http://www.mtv.com/news/1550536/dreamgirls-leads-oscar-noms-without-best-picture-or-beyonce/}}</ref>。截至[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|2014年]]，《梦女孩》仍然是仅有的一部获提名数量最多，但其中却没有最佳影片奖提名的电影<ref>{{cite news | last = Rea | first = Steven | title = Oscar hugs and shrugs The Academy Award nominations show unusual diversity this year and, in the case of "Dreamgirls," an oddity. Oscar is doing his part for diversity | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | date = 2007-01-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140219090403/http://articles.philly.com/2007-01-24/news/25220650_1_time-in-oscar-history-directors-guild-nominations-fourth-best-picture-nomination | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | archivedate = 2014-02-19 | url = http://articles.philly.com/2007-01-24/news/25220650_1_time-in-oscar-history-directors-guild-nominations-fourth-best-picture-nomination | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

获奖名单在2007年2月25日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news | title = Nominees & Winners for the 79th Academy Awards | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-2009/79nominees.html | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = AMPAS | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201163346/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-2009/79nominees.html | archivedate = 2014-02-01}}</ref>。获[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|影帝]]提名的[[彼得·奥图尔|彼得·奥图尔]]仍然未能获奖，成为从未胜出演员中获提名次数最多的一位<ref>{{cite news | title = Peter O'Toole | publisher = Gannett Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202222446/http://archive.indystar.com/usatoday/article/4031975 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | url = http://archive.indystar.com/usatoday/article/4031975 | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = The Indianapolis Star | date = 2013-12-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。获[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角奖]]的[[詹妮弗·哈德森|詹妮弗·哈德森]]成为历史上第十五位凭电影处女作获奖的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = Montgomery | first = Daniel | title = Will Lupita Nyongo and Barkhad Abdi join 15 Oscar winners for film debuts? | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = Gold Derby | date = 2014-01-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201195348/http://www.goldderby.com/news/5519/oscars-lupita-nyongo-12-years-a-slave-barkhad-abdi-captain-phillips-news-93526841.html | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.goldderby.com/news/5519/oscars-lupita-nyongo-12-years-a-slave-barkhad-abdi-captain-phillips-news-93526841.html}}</ref>。《难以忽视的真相》插曲“{{lang|en|I Need to Wake Up}}”成为第一首获[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|原创歌曲奖]]的[[纪录片|纪录片]]插曲<ref>{{cite news | title = The 79th Academy Awards (2007) Ceremony Overview | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140328060420/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/79th.html | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/79th.html | accessdate = 2014-05-15 | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = AMPAS | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-28}}</ref>。

