== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Ellen_DeGeneres_2011.jpg|130px]]担任第79届奥斯卡颁奖典礼主持人]]
由于之前几届颁奖典礼收视率有所下滑，美国电影艺术与科学学院试图对节目作出变革，重燃观众对提名电影的兴趣。2006年9月，学院选择[[制片人|制片人]]劳拉·泽斯金负责本届晚会的制作，这也是她第二次担任奥斯卡颁奖典礼的制作人<ref>{{cite news | last = Archerd | first = Army | title = Oscar gig for Ziskin | archivedate = 2014-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140303101044/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/oscar-gig-for-ziskin-1200339437/ | url = http://variety.com/2006/film/news/oscar-gig-for-ziskin-1200339437/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2006-07-20}}</ref>。近三个月后，曾在2001至2005年间三度主持[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的女演员艾伦·德杰尼勒斯获选成为颁奖典礼的[[主持人|主持人]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Vries | first = Lloyd | title = Ellen DeGeneres to Host the Oscars | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221065628/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/ellen-degeneres-to-host-the-oscars/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/ellen-degeneres-to-host-the-oscars/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = CBS News | publisher = CBS Corporation | date = 2006-09-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-21}}</ref>。泽斯金在接受《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》采访时表示，她是因为相信德杰尼勒斯一定能够在节目收视率上有所助益而做此决定的，她在各个族群中都吃得开，也受到很大范围观众群的青睐。学院主席甘尼斯也称赞德杰尼勒斯精力充沛，既聪明又爽朗<ref>{{cite news | last = Welkos | first = Robert W. | title = Everybody likes Ellen, especially Oscar | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2006/sep/09/entertainment/et-ellen9 | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2006-09-09 | archivedate = 2013-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222050812/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/sep/09/entertainment/et-ellen9 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

美国电影艺术与科学学院将这个夜晚的主题定为电影对白的庆典<ref name="Quotes">{{cite news | title = Movie Quotes Line the Road to Oscars | url = http://oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2007/07.01.25.html | accessdate = 2008-12-11 | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = AMPAS | date = 2007-01-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081211094900/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2007/07.01.25.html | archivedate = 2008-12-11}}</ref>。为了配合这一主题，[[广告代理商|广告代理商]]“{{lang|en|TBWA\Chiat\Day}}”设计了晚会的官方海报，其上包含有75句来自不同奥斯卡提名和获奖电影中的台词<ref>{{cite news | last = Sneider | first = Jeff | title = Oscar poster lines 'em up | url = http://variety.com/2006/film/news/oscar-poster-lines-em-up-1117956079/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304224554/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/oscar-poster-lines-em-up-1117956079/ | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2006-12-19 | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。电影人[[史派克·李|史派克·李]]制作了一段预告片，其中展示了许多[[纽约|纽约]]周边平常百姓把一些知名电影台词脱口而出的情景<ref name="Quotes" />。晚会期间播放了导演[[南茜·迈耶斯|南茜·迈耶斯]]制作的一段视频片段，其中向[[剧作家|剧作家]]的工作致敬，对他们在电影事业中的贡献表示敬意<ref>{{cite news | last = White | first = Dave | title = Oscars: Even more bloated than 'Idol' | url = http://www.today.com/id/17333639/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/oscars-even-more-bloated-idol/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = NBC News | publisher = NBCUniversal | date = 2007-02-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222140453/http://www.today.com/id/17333639/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/oscars-even-more-bloated-idol/ | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Fernandez | first = Jay A. | title = A step toward recognizing where it starts | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2007/feb/28/entertainment/et-scriptland28 | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2007-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304061217/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/feb/28/entertainment/et-scriptland28}}</ref>。

电视直播期间，美国前[[美国副总统|副总统]]，环保活动人士[[阿尔·戈尔|阿尔·戈尔]]和获男主角奖提名的演员[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]宣布，学院将在颁奖典礼中融入多项有关环境和生态意识的内容<ref>{{cite news | title = Natural Resources Defense Council "Greens" the Academy Awards | url = http://www.nrdc.org/media/2007/070225.asp | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Natural Resources Defense Council | publisher = NDRC |date = 2007-02-25 | archivedate = 2013-10-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001202450/http://www.nrdc.org/media/2007/070225.asp | deadurl = no}}</ref>。由弗兰克·韦伯（{{lang|en|Frank Webb}}）和马修·怀特（{{lang|en|Matthew White}}）设计，供颁奖嘉宾和获奖者在后台休息的《[[建筑文摘|建筑文摘]]》（{{lang|en|''Architectural Digest''}}）演员休息室中，就包含有多项环保特色，例如用回收塑料瓶制作的地毯，没有使用任何[[挥发性有机化合物|挥发性有机化合物]]染料绘制的墙壁等<ref>{{cite news | last = Puente | first = Maria | title = It's stylish, it's lavish, it's ... the greenroom? | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-14-oscar-greenroom_x.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221065744/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-14-oscar-greenroom_x.htm | date = 2007-02-14 | archivedate = 2014-02-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。其他环保方面的举措还包括：使用[[混合动力电动汽车|混合动力电动汽车]]向晚会嘉宾提供运输服务，利用回收纸制作选票和邀请函，在主席大厅提供的膳食配备的是可重复使用的盘子和可生物降解的餐具<ref>{{cite news | last = Faber | first = Judy | title = No Statue, But A Win Nonetheless For Gore | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/no-statue-but-a-win-nonetheless-for-gore/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = CBS News | publisher = CBS Corporation | date = 2007-02-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222212635/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/no-statue-but-a-win-nonetheless-for-gore/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

另外还有多人参与了颁奖典礼的制作。威廉·罗斯（{{lang|en|William Ross}}）担任晚会的音乐总监<ref>{{cite news | last = Sneider | first = Jeff | title = Black, Keaton added to Oscars | publisher = PMC | date = 2007-02-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228031717/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/black-keaton-added-to-oscars-1117959866/ | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/black-keaton-added-to-oscars-1117959866/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Variety | archivedate = 2014-02-28}}</ref>。[[J·迈克尔·里瓦|J·迈克尔·里瓦]]（{{lang|en|J. Michael Riva}}）设计制作了新的舞台和布景<ref>{{cite news | last = Repstad | first = Laura | title = Riva tapped as production designer | publisher = PMC | date = 2006-12-28 | url = http://variety.com/2006/film/news/riva-tapped-as-production-designer-1117956397/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140301051916/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/riva-tapped-as-production-designer-1117956397/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Variety | archivedate = 2014-03-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[配音演员|配音演员]][[唐·拉方丹|唐·拉方丹]]（{{lang|en|Don LaFontaine}}）和[[吉娜·塔特尔|吉娜·塔特尔]]（{{lang|en|Gina Tuttle}}）一起获聘成为颁奖典礼的电视广播员<ref>{{cite book | last = Terrance | first = Vincent | title = Television Specials: 5,336 Entertainment Programs, 1936–2012 | url = https://archive.org/details/televisionspecia0000terr_h3f6 | year = 2013 | isbn = 978-0-7864-7444-8 | location = Jefferson, North Carolina, United States | edition = 2nd |oclc= | publisher = McFarland & Company | page = [https://archive.org/details/televisionspecia0000terr_h3f6/page/14 14]}}</ref>。男演员[[格雷格·沃恩|格雷格·沃恩]]与《[[幸运_(杂志)|幸运]]》（{{lang|en|''Lucky''}}）[[杂志|杂志]]专栏作家阿利森·沃特曼一起在奥斯卡金像奖网站上主持每周一期的幕后视频博客《奥斯卡之路》（{{lang|en|''Road to the Oscars''}}）<ref name="Allyson" />。皮洛伯洛斯舞团成员现场表演了对获提名电影片名及镜头加以诠释的特别节目<ref>{{cite news | last = Keck | first = William | title = A star is born in shape- shifting Pilobolus | archivedate = 2014-02-20 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-22-pilobolus_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2007-02-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220044141/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-22-pilobolus_x.htm}}</ref>。[[杰克·布莱克|杰克·布莱克]]、[[威尔·法瑞尔|威尔·法瑞尔]]和[[约翰·C·赖利|约翰·C·赖利]]三位男演员表演了一段轻快的歌舞曲目，该曲目由导演[[贾德·阿帕图|贾德·阿帕图]]和[[作曲家|作曲家]][[马克·施艾曼|马克·施艾曼]]（{{lang|en|Marc Shaiman}}）共同创作，对奥斯卡金像奖不重视[[喜剧|喜剧]]的现象加以嘲讽<ref>{{cite news | last = Apatow | first = Judd | title = Apatow recalls working with Shaiman | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/apatow-recalls-working-with-shaiman-1117968231/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2007-07-09 | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304225442/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/apatow-recalls-working-with-shaiman-1117968231/}}</ref>。[[音效合唱团|音效合唱团]]经音乐家史蒂夫·西德维尔（{{lang|en|Steve Sidwell}}）指挥，在现场播放一段经典电影蒙太奇时表演了一段嗓音音效<ref>{{cite web | title = Composer {{!}} Steve Sidwell | archivedate = 2014-04-19 | deadurl = no | work = Universal Music Publishing Group | publisher = NBCUniversal | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419231058/http://www.unippmglobal.com/#/composers/Composers%20Q-Z/Barnaby%20Taylor.aspx | url = http://www.unippmglobal.com/#/composers/Composers%20Q-Z/Barnaby%20Taylor.aspx}}</ref>。晚会开场时播放了一段由纪录片导演[[埃洛·莫里斯|埃洛·莫里斯]]制作的片段，其中有多位获得提名的电影人对提名的意义加以探讨<ref>{{cite news | last = Thompson | first = Anne | title = Morris cuts it close with his Oscar docu | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140516154006/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/morris-cuts-close-his-oscar-130781 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/morris-cuts-close-his-oscar-130781 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2007-02-23 | page = 6 | archivedate = 2014-05-16}}</ref>。意大利导演[[朱賽貝·托納多雷|朱賽貝·托納多雷]]制作了一段向过去获得过[[奥斯卡最佳外语片奖|外语片奖]]电影致敬的片段<ref>{{cite news|last=Susman |first=Gary |title=Oscars '07: 10 Memorable Moments |archivedate=2014-02-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222132042/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20009747_20013925%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20009747_20013925,00.html |accessdate=2014-05-16 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner |date=2007-02-27 }}</ref>。电影制作人[[麦克尔·曼|麦克尔·曼]]还制作了一段从电影中了解美国社会生活的视频片段<ref>{{cite news | last = Kennedy | first = Lisa | title = An icon gets his due, but not for best work | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222132042/http://www.denverpost.com/colleges/ci_5305931?source=pkg | deadurl = no | url = http://www.denverpost.com/colleges/ci_5305931?source=pkg | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = The Denver Post | publisher = MediaNews Group | date = 2007-02-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-22}}</ref>。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截至1月23日提名公布时，全部5部获最佳影片奖提名电影的总计[[票房|票房]]收入为2亿4365万2345[[美元|美元]]，平均每部4873万零469美元<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars">{{cite news | title = 2006 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2006&p=.htm | accessdate = January 30, 2014 | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = Amazon.com | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503031228/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2006&p=.htm}}</ref>。其中《无间道风云》以1亿2175万6022美元位居榜首，其后分别是收入5959万4615美元的《阳光小美女》，进账3586万8000美元的《女王》，收入2383万8933美元的《通天塔》和进账259万4775美元的《硫磺岛的来信》<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars" />。

在2006年美国电影票房50强中，有9部电影获得了共计29项提名。其中《当幸福来敲门》（第12名）、《波拉特》（第15名）、《穿普拉达的女王》（第16名）、《无间道风云》（第17位》和《梦女孩》（第28位）获得了最佳影片、导演、动画长片或是任意一项演员、编剧类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars2006">{{cite news | title = 2007 Domestic Grosses (as of January 23, 2007) | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = Amazon.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201194935/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2007-01-23&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2006&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2007-01-23&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2006&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm}}</ref>。另外4部获提名的电影分别是《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》（[[冠军|冠军]]）、《赛车总动员》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《超人归来》（第6名）和《快乐的大脚》（第8名）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars2006" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本场晚会所获媒体评价褒贬不一。一些媒体的评价较为负面，例如《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的蒂姆·古德曼哀叹节目漫长而平淡，臃肿且无聊。他指出，人们收看奥斯卡颁奖典礼时往往期待看到流行且单刀直入的幽默，但主持人德杰尼勒斯的幽默风格却是含蓄且散漫的，所以不符合观众的预期<ref>{{cite news | last = Goodman | first = Tim | title = Departed evening of bloated, boring Hollywood babble | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Hearst Corporation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222022246/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/THE-79TH-ACADEMY-AWARDS-Departed-evening-of-2646004.php | date = 2007-02-25 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/THE-79TH-ACADEMY-AWARDS-Departed-evening-of-2646004.php}}</ref>。《[[丹佛邮报|丹佛邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Denver Post''}}）电视评论员乔安妮·奥斯特鲁夫（{{lang|en|Joanne Ostrow}}）则认为，这总体上是一场“无害且让人愉快”的晚会，“但却几乎完全没有兴奋点，德杰尼勒斯忘记了奥斯卡颁奖典礼主持人的首要原则：这不是真的让你来主持。好莱坞最盛大的夜晚（也是电视上第二盛大的夜晚，仅次于[[超级碗|超级碗]]）应该是一场电影的庆典”<ref>{{cite news | last = Ostrow | first = Joanne | title = Mediocre Ellen lowers telecast to daytime | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222062701/http://www.denverpost.com/opinion/ci_5305942 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | url = http://www.denverpost.com/opinion/ci_5305942 | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = The Denver Post | publisher = MediaNews Group | date = 2007-02-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》专栏作家汤姆·谢尔斯（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）认为德杰尼勒斯的表现还过得去，但批评节目总体进展缓慢，节奏有欠连贯，并且时间实在太长，感觉就是一种折磨<ref>{{cite news | last = Shales | first = Tom | title = The Broadcast: Long and Longer | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/02/26/AR2007022600027.html | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = The Washington Post | publisher = The Washington Post Company | date = 2007-02-26 | archive-date = 2013-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130907082344/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/02/26/AR2007022600027.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

其它媒体对节目的评价更为正面。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》专栏作家亚历山德拉·斯坦利（{{lang|en|Alessandra Stanley}}）称赞了主持人的表现，称她“（虽说）脸皮甚厚，但心地善良，远不像[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|去年]]的[[乔恩·斯图尔特|乔恩·斯图尔特]]和[[第77届奥斯卡金像奖|2005年]]的[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]那么尖酸刻薄。”斯坦利还称，德杰尼勒斯的主持风格给这个花哨的周日带来了星期五的休闲感<ref>{{cite news | last = Stanley | first = Alessandra | title = Bringing a Touch of Daytime to Hollywood's Biggest Night | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/02/26/arts/television/26watc.html?_r=1& | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2007-02-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309080735/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/02/26/arts/television/26watc.html?_r=1& | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-09}}</ref>。《[[圣路易斯邮报|圣路易斯邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''St. Louis Post-Dispatch''}}）电视评论员盖尔·潘宁顿（{{lang|en|Gail Pennnington}}）称赞主持人德杰尼勒斯和制片人泽斯金把这个夜晚变成了“一场乐观的庆祝活动，也是多年来最具娱乐性的奥斯卡颁奖典礼”<ref>{{cite news | last = Pennington | first = Gail | title = DeGeneres kept the Oscar show upbeat and lively | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = St. Louis Post-Dispatch | publisher = Lee Enterprises | date = 2007-02-26 | page = D1 | url = http://business.highbeam.com/435553/article-1G1-159838567/degeneres-kept-oscar-show-upbeat-and-lively | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140516150041/http://business.highbeam.com/435553/article-1G1-159838567/degeneres-kept-oscar-show-upbeat-and-lively | archivedate = 2014-05-16 | deadurl = yes | via = HighBeam Research }}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶每日新闻|洛杉矶每日新闻]]》（{{lang|en|''Los Angeles Daily News''}}）电视栏目主编戴夫·克朗克（{{lang|en|Dave Kronke}}）对主持人的表现予以高度评价，称她在段子上选材上佳，态度和蔼可亲，让这个夜晚不仅成为获奖者的庆祝活动，更令所有提名人都能够乐在其中<ref>{{cite news | last = Kronke | first = David | title = Yep, She's Funny Gentle Humor wins for DeGeneres | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Los Angeles Daily News | publisher = MediaNews Group | date = 2007-02-26 | page = U8 | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-9111119.html | via = HighBeam Research | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140629075625/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-9111119.html | archive-date = 2014-06-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

=== 收视率和奖项 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有3992万观众收看，与[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|前一年]]相比提高了2.5%<ref>{{cite web | first = Bill | last = Gorman | title = Academy Awards Averages 41.3 Million Viewers; Most Since 2005 | archivedate = 2013-11-01 | deadurl = yes | publisher = TVbytheNumbers | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ | date = 2010-03-08 | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131101231748/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Rich | first = Joshua | title = A few lingering Oscar curiosities | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/27/a_few_lingering/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2007-02-27 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202095850/http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/27/a_few_lingering/}}</ref>，而所有曾观看部分时段节目的观众总数则估计有7672万<ref name="Nikki Finke Oscar ratings" />。从尼尔森收视率调查的数据看，节目的表现也好过去年，吸引了23.6%的人群收看，收视率达到38.86%<ref name="TVB Oscars">{{cite news|title=Academy Awards ratings |work=Television Bureau of Advertising |format=PDF |archivedate=2013-10-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016061652/http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |accessdate=2014-05-16 |url=http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外节目也在18至49岁年龄段观众群中收获了14.18 / 33.71的收视率，这意味着全美所有18至49岁年龄段人群里有14.18%观看了颁奖典礼，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有33.71%选择收看这个节目<ref>{{cite news | last = Gough | first = Paul J. | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/strong-week-abc-but-idol-131032 | title = Strong week for ABC, but 'Idol' lifts Fox | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140317004719/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/strong-week-abc-but-idol-131032 | date = 2007-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-03-17}}</ref>。

2007年7月，颁奖典礼获得了第59届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的9项提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Primetime Emmy Award Database | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/79th-annual-academy-awards | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences | publisher = ATAS | archivedate = 2013-12-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131225112423/http://www.emmys.com/shows/79th-annual-academy-awards}}</ref>，并在两个月后赢得了最佳艺术指导奖和最佳音乐指导奖<ref>{{cite news | title = List of Emmy Winners 2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208042639/http://www.tvweek.com/news/2007/09/list_emmy_winners_2007.php | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvweek.com/news/2007/09/list_emmy_winners_2007.php | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Television Week | publisher = Crain Communications | date = 2007-09-16 | archivedate = 2012-02-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = The complete list of winners | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/17/entertainment/et-emmywinners17 | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2007-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222212304/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/17/entertainment/et-emmywinners17 | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 纪念 ==
奥斯卡颁奖典礼上一年一度的“纪念”致敬环节旨在纪念过去一年中逝世的业内人士，本场晚会上的这一环节由女演员[[朱迪·福斯特|朱迪·福斯特]]引出，纪念了以下人士：<ref>{{cite news | last = Kirschling | first = Gregory | title = Live-blogging the Oscars, baby! | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/26/liveblogging_th_1/ | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2007-02-26 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202100144/http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/02/26/liveblogging_th_1/}}</ref>

